' SD-04. UC-004 방향 전환 후 청소 재개
' Related Use Case: UC-004. 방향 전환 후 청소 재개
' Intent: 방향 전환 완료 후 전방 이동 가능 여부를 확인하고 전진 청소 상태로 복귀하는 흐름을 표현한다.
' Note: 먼지 대응 상태가 유지 중이면 증가 출력 상태를 일반 출력으로 덮어쓰지 않는다.

@startuml SD_04_UC004_Resume_After_Turn
title SD-04 - UC-004 방향 전환 후 청소 재개

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "DustResponse" as DustResponse
participant "CleaningPolicy" as Policy
participant "CleaningCommand" as CleaningCommand
participant "MovementCommand" as MovementCommand
actor "주행 장치" as Drive
actor "청소 장치" as Cleaner

Sensor -> Controller: reportFrontObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=false)
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: updateFrontObstacle(frontObstacleDetected=false)
Controller -> Cleaning: resumeAfterTurn(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: isFrontObstacleDetected()
SensorState --> Cleaning: false
Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(MOVE_FORWARD)
MovementCommand --> Cleaning: moveForwardCommand
Cleaning -> Cleaning: changeMovementStatus(CLEANING)

alt 먼지 대응 상태 유지 중
    Cleaning -> DustResponse: isActive()
    DustResponse --> Cleaning: true
    Cleaning -> DustResponse: currentPowerLevel()
    DustResponse --> Cleaning: INCREASED
    Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(moveForwardCommand, keepPower=INCREASED)
    Controller -> Cleaner: keepCleaningPower(INCREASED)
else 일반 청소 상태
    Cleaning -> Policy: normalPowerLevel()
    Policy --> Cleaning: NORMAL
    Cleaning -> CleaningCommand: create(NORMAL)
    CleaningCommand --> Cleaning: cleaningCommand
    Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(moveForwardCommand, cleaningCommand)
    Controller -> Cleaner: setCleaningPower(NORMAL)
end

Controller -> Drive: moveForward()
Cleaning --> Controller: resumed()

alt 방향 전환 후 전방 장애물 재감지
    Sensor -> Controller: reportObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected, rightObstacleDetected)
    Controller -> SensorState: updateObstacles(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected, rightObstacleDetected)
    Controller -> Cleaning: selectAvoidanceDirection(SensorState)
    note right of Cleaning: 좌우 장애물 상태를 포함해 UC-003을 다시 수행
end

deactivate Cleaning
deactivate Controller
@enduml
